	<div class="sp-template-desc">
	
	<h1>Findborg Comet</h1>
	Joomla 3.0 Template Framework by <a target="_blank" href="http://www.findborg.com">www.findborg.com</a>.
	
	<h3>This Is Base Template</h3>
	Premium and powerfull Joomla templates and Extensions.<br /><a href="http://www.findborg.com" target="_blank">http://www.findborg.com</a><br /><br />See a live demo of all templates created by Findborg.<br /><a href="http://demo.findborg.com" target="_blank">http://demo.findborg.com</a><br />
	
	<h2>Overview of the Comet Framework</h2>
	Imagine yourself dwelling in a world of super fast website building capacity. You just see it fully grown up even before you feel that you have just started building it! The Comet Framework is here to make you feel the difference in the world of website designing. This product has been developed by Findborg, your trusted friend in the Joomla world, for an easy accessibility to the way of building Joomla based websites with hundreds of easy tasking features.
	<br />
	<br />
	What does the Comet Framework intend to do? Well, it is pretty simple - it will make your experience of creating website much smoother than ever before. Comet Framework aims to make many of the time consuming activities that you have to deal with when creating a Joomla based site and package them right up at your finger tips,  so that you can create highly sophisticated websites in less time.
	</div>
